        <div class="card-body">
            <h5 class="card-title fs-4">Project Title: Simple User Management System</h5>
            <p class="card-text fs-5"><strong>Overview: </strong>This project is a user management system designed to
                streamline the process
                of managing customer information. Built using a combination of modern web technologies, it allows users
                to add, view, update, and delete customer details efficiently.</p>
